00:06:47.050 --> 00:06:49.370
&gt;&gt; Alexi Kenney: I mean
I guess we all come at it

00:06:49.370 --> 00:06:53.610
from different places, but
eventually at the end of the day

00:06:53.610 --> 00:07:02.690
for me collaboration is king in
music, so all experiences stem

00:07:02.690 --> 00:07:05.820
from chamber music in my opinion.

00:07:05.820 --> 00:07:08.800
