00:11:24.590 --> 00:11:26.870
It's not one of these, you know --

00:11:26.870 --> 00:11:28.170
&gt;&gt;

00:11:28.170 --> 00:11:29.470
&gt;&gt; Nicholas Brown: Yeah.

